was\
the\
second\
declaration\
of\
independence\
by\
Kosovo's\
[[Albanian\
people|Albanian]]-dominated\
political\
institutions,\
the\
first\
having\
been\
proclaimed\
on\
[[7\
September]]\
[[1990]].&lt;ref&gt;Howard\
Clark,\
