members\
of\
the\
[[Kosovo\
Assembly]]\
meeting\
in\
[[Pristina]],\
the\
capital\
of\
Kosovo,\
on\
[[17\
February]]\
[[2008]].\
It\
was\
approved\
by\
a\
show\
of\
hands,\
with\
no\
votes\
of\
opposition\
from\
the\
109\
members\
present.\
Ten\
Assembly\
members,\
including\
all\
the\
Kosovo\
Serbs,\
